sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor S1 as Student 1
    participant F as Frontend (React)
    participant W as WebSocket Server (FastAPI)
    participant R as Redis (Pub/Sub)
    actor S2 as Student 2 (In Room)

    S1->>F: Types message & clicks "Send"
    F->>W: Sends JSON over WebSocket (type: "room_message")
    W->>R: Publishes message to room channel
    R-->>W: Broadcasts to all server workers
    W-->>F: Sends message back to Student 1
    F-->>S1: Updates chat UI
    W-->>S2: Sends message over WebSocket
    S2-->>S2: Updates chat UI
